author: kylem
msg: Added method parameter name and annotation accessors to ControlBeanContext APIs.  It's now
possible to include parameter name as part of extensible control semantics, and to extract
parameter values by name from within an extensible method invocation.  Also included are three
new checkin tests that verify accessor APIs.
